==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|grc}} '''[[μελαγχολία]]''' (''melancholia'') " atrabiliousness", from '''[[μέλας]]''' ''[[μελαν-]]'' (''melas'', ''melan-'') "black, dark, murky" + '''[[χολή]]''' (''chole'') "bile". Compare the Latin {{term|atra bilis|ātra bīlis|black bile|lang=la}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|US}} {{IPA|/ˈmɛl.ənˌkɑl.i/}}

===Adjective===
{{en-adj}}

